title: Biden Victory Means 4 Years of Trump Support Wasted for UK-US Trade Deal
description:
Watch the full episode here:  https://www.lotuseaters.com/the-podcast-of-the-lotus-eaters-episode-1-09-11-20

Meaning the UK's chance to get a deal with the supportive Donald Trump might have been wasted.
